headline: Fifth Third Is Merging Its Wealth Business With Comerica’s. That Creates Uncertainty for Ameriprise.
summary: It remains unclear whether the deal to create the nation’s ninth largest bank would end Comerica’s brokerage-service deal with Ameriprise.
